UES , Russia work on convertible issue . Russia ' s Privatisation Ministry and national electricity company Unified Energy System ( UES ) are working on a scheme to sell a 1 . 5 percent government - owned stake of UES through a convertible bond , probably this autumn , privatisation minister Alfred Kokh said on Thursday . " We have formed a working group together with UES which is developing a scheme to sell a 1 . 5 percent stake in the form of convertible securities , " he told a news conference . He said he expected the plan to be ready by autumn . 
